class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Infrastructure\\Mercure\\RunEventPublisher"
type: final class
summary: "The RunEventPublisher class publishes domain RunEvent instances to a Mercure hub using configurable serialization and topic policies. It implements a coalescing mechanism to batch rapid updates within a defined time window, reducing unnecessary network traffic."
